summary: Simple .bat file with dos commands to remove most of enb profiles from your skyrim folder.
descriptionHtml:
Description:
Simple .bat file with dos commands to remove most of enb profiles from your skyrim folder.

Instalation:
Unpack to ../skyrim/ folder and double click enb_remover_by_olbins.bat

Other notes:
It does NOT remove anything from ../skyrim/data/ folder. So no .esp .bsa texture and meshes won't be removed. They have to be removed manually.
I know its very simple bat file and any user with minimum computer knowlege can do it all alone but i saved you the troubles :)
You can remove manually anything from the bat file if you don't want to remove for example .dll files.
I don't know all the files that are included in every enb preset so if something missing then give me a call and I'll add.

Permission.
You can distribute the file with your own enb preset but at least giving me a little credit would make me happy :)

Cheers.
author: olbins
